HEADWORD: Tottle
<hw>Tot"tle</hw> <pr>(t⟦ocr⟧t"t'l)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos>
<vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p. p.</pos> <conjf>Tottled</conjf>
